title: Incident that occurred in the vicinity of Wayne Elementary School (City of Radnor, PA)
text: ( Source : City of Radnor, PA ) On Wednesday evening, October 21 , 2015 shortly after 6:30 PM Radnor Police received a 9-1-1 call reporting that an Asian male had approached 3 juveniles at the intersection of W. Wayne and Arbordale Avenues .
